{"ts":"2026-07-19T03:43:35.546Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"append","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"GH-612. --acceptance-criteria/--ac replaces the whole value; repeatable only within one invocation (joins with '; ' per pm-b84u). Across calls/branches, two agents each adding a criterion clobber the base and conflict on the single acceptance_criteria line. Fix: --add-ac/--remove-ac individual-criterion operations (tag-API parity), replace semantics unchanged for --ac; disjoint additions merge cleanly across branches (pm-m3nl scalar-line caveat applies)."},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-19T03:43:35.546Z"}],"before_hash":"0ba01c00a1a50ebd93f4d60b94364ebd1e7bbc97b66821d40500be781060de65","after_hash":"8bb42ce79fd48997803d98704d5464183cc14070362de3be86b0d18efc02d227"}
